channel.title: Help with somthink
channel.description:
say that i have silb client and mopar and i wanted to change the pictures for my own use ONLY how would i do this?

links or tuts would be great

item.title: Help with somthink
item.dc:creator: @Dark_Danger Dark Danger
item.description:
@Dark_Danger wrote:

Well you would need to download a client source first, then you would need to go and save a pic the name of your client in the client folder then open the client.java file

you will see a lil code for a pic (im not at home atm so i couldnt tell you what code)

search for image or img in the file, then replace the “” with “(your picture name.(what ever extension it is))”

i will help more when i get home.

kktyvm
